T1  - THE RETURN TO COLLEGE: SELECTION AND DROPOUT RISK
AU  - Hendricks, Lutz
AU  - Leukhina, Oksana
Y1  - 2018/08/01
PY  - 2018
DA  - 2018/08/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/iere.12297
