T1  - THE ENDOWMENT EFFECT AS BLESSING
AU  - Frenkel, Sivan
AU  - Heller, Yuval
AU  - Teper, Roee
Y1  - 2018/08/01
PY  - 2018
DA  - 2018/08/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/iere.12300
