T1  - PUBLIC GOOD PROVISION WITH CONSTITUTIONAL CONSTRAINT
AU  - Rong, Kang
Y1  - 2018/08/01
PY  - 2018
DA  - 2018/08/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/iere.12301
T2  - International Economic Review
JF  - International Economic Review
JO  - International Economic Review
