T1  - MEDICAID AND THE LABOR SUPPLY OF SINGLE MOTHERS: IMPLICATIONS FOR HEALTH CARE REFORM
AU  - Pohl, R. Vincent
Y1  - 2018/08/01
PY  - 2018
DA  - 2018/08/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/iere.12304
