T1  - TAYLOR PROJECTION: A NEW SOLUTION METHOD FOR DYNAMIC GENERAL EQUILIBRIUM MODELS
AU  - Levintal, Oren
Y1  - 2018/08/01
PY  - 2018
DA  - 2018/08/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/iere.12306
T2  - International Economic Review
